'''宾厄姆顿枪击案'''（Binghamton shootings）是于2009年4月3日星期五发生在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[宾厄姆顿|宾厄姆顿]]市中心的[[美国公民协会|美国公民协会]][[移民美国|移民服务中心]]的[[枪击|枪击]]事件。

[[北美东部时区|美国东部时间]]4月3日上午10:30左右，一名[[越裔美國人|越南裔]]移民吉韦利·王（Jiverly Wong）<ref name="reutersapril4"/><ref name="nytimesblog">{{cite news|url=http://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/04/03/shooting-in-binghamton/|title=Shooting in Binghamton, N.Y.|last=Seelye|first=Katharine Q|date=April 3, 2009|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180211193206/https://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/04/03/shooting-in-binghamton/|archive-date=2018-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>闯入该移民服务中心，见人便开枪，<ref name="ABC2">{{Cite news
| title = Negotiators Work to Save Victims and Suspects – ABC News
| date = 2009-04-03
| accessdate = April 3, 2009
| url = http://abcnews.go.com/US/story?id=7250177&page=1
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190408115806/https://abcnews.go.com/US/story?id=7250177&page=1
| archive-date = 2019-04-08
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>造成包括凶手在内的14人死亡，<ref name ="abcnews">{{cite news|url = http://abcnews.go.com/US/story?id=7249853&page=1|title = Binghamton Rampage Leaves 14 Dead, Police Don't Know Motive|date = April 3, 2009|accessdate = April 3, 2009|publisher = [[ABC_News|ABC News]]|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190405114542/https://abcnews.go.com/US/story?id=7249853&page=1|archive-date = 2019-04-05|dead-url = no}}</ref>4人受伤。<ref name="reutersapril4">{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/topNews/idUSTRE5324JP20090404| title=Police say N.Y. immigrant shooter's act no surprise| date=2009-04-04| publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]| accessdate=2009-04-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090405144311/http://www.reuters.com/article/topNews/idUSTRE5324JP20090404| archive-date=2009-04-05| dead-url=no}}</ref>凶手还曾挟持41人作人质。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/CRIME/04/03/binghamton.shooting/index.html|title=Official: Hostages held after 'multiple' shootings|date=April 3, 2009|accessdate=April 3, 2009|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406053922/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/CRIME/04/03/binghamton.shooting/index.html|archive-date=2009-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

美国公民协会移民服务中心是一个为[[移民|移民]]和[[难民|难民]]提供服务的机构，当时这个中心里有五十余人，其中多数是前来上公民课或英语课的移民。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.unitedwaybroome.org/pages/Member%20Agencies/American_Civic_Association.htm|date=March 3, 2009|publisher=unitedwaybroome.org|title=United Way, Member Agencies: American Civic Association|accessdate=April 3, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090311084049/http://unitedwaybroome.org/pages/Member%20Agencies/American_Civic_Association.htm|archivedate=2009年3月11日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqgj/2009-04/05/content_7649700.htm|title=美国纽约州枪击案致14人死亡 奥巴马夫妇震惊|publisher=中国日报|date=2009-04-05|accessdate=2009-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408221039/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqgj/2009-04/05/content_7649700.htm|archive-date=2009-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==凶手资料==
枪击案的凶手吉韦利·王（Jiverly Wong），别名Jiverly Voong，原名王领发（音译自Voong Linh Phat），42岁，[[越裔美国人|越南裔美国人]]，居住于距离宾厄姆顿3英里的[[約翰遜城_(紐約州)|約翰遜城]]。<ref name="nytimesblog"/><ref name="ny man">{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/WireStory?id=7255244&page=1|title=NY Gunman Angry Over Poor English Skills, Job Loss|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-04-04|accessdate=2009-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404232455/http://abcnews.go.com/US/WireStory?id=7255244&page=1|archive-date=2009-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kates2">{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gJkIIKfdTrpMZyiQPW7SWmCNR2HAD97BLLMG0|title=NY gunman angry over poor English skills, job loss|last=Kates|first=William|date=April 4, 2009|publisher=Associated Press|accessdate=April 4, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408011556/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gJkIIKfdTrpMZyiQPW7SWmCNR2HAD97BLLMG0|archive-date=2009-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>王生于越南的一个[[越南华人|华人家庭]]，<ref name="press">{{cite news|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090404/ap_on_re_us/binghamton_shootings|title=As gunman's life fell apart, he took others'|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=2009-04-04|date=2009-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090412214624/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090404/ap_on_re_us/binghamton_shootings|archive-date=2009-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>80年代初期来到美国纽约州，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jfdaily.com/news/xwgj/200904/t20090405_594677.htm|title=纽约州枪击案动机成谜 官方否认与恐怖主义有关|work=新闻晚报|publisher=解放网|date=2009-04-05|accessdate=2009-04-06}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>然后搬到[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]居住。1992年，因涉嫌诈骗被警方逮捕。1995年11月，王加入美国籍。此后不久离开美国。1999年12月回到[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]。居住于加州期间，王曾与蒋秀萍（音译自Xiu Ping Jiang）结婚，但不久后离婚。<ref name="FOXNews">{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,512605,00.html|title=Families Bury Binghamton, N.Y. Shooting Victims; New Details Emerge About Gunman|publisher=FOX News|date=2009-04-05|accessdate=2009-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406181435/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,512605,00.html|archive-date=2009-04-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>两人没有子女。<ref name="wife">{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/ny_crime/2009/04/05/2009-04-05_no_way_police_could_have_saved_jiverly_w.html|title=No way police could have saved Jiverly Wong's 13 Binghamton victims, officials say|publisher=New York Daily News|date=2009-04-05|accessdate=2009-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090407093950/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/ny_crime/2009/04/05/2009-04-05_no_way_police_could_have_saved_jiverly_w.html|archive-date=2009-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

王曾在加州[[英格爾伍德_(加利福尼亞州)|英格尔伍德市]]居住。居住期间，曾在洛杉矶一家名为''Kikka Sushi''的寿司店当了将近七年的送货员。 

对于之前称王曾被[[纽约|纽约]]{{tsl|en|Endicott, New York|恩迪科特}}村附近一家[[IBM|IBM]]解雇的报道，<ref name = "abcnews"/><ref name="Kates2"/>IBM方面表示，记录显示公司没雇过吉韦利·王，在这家公司工作的是他的父亲亨利·王。<ref name="Kates2"/>一位自称是亨利之女的人表示，她兄弟吉韦利曾在一家吸尘器公司''Shop Vac''工作，一直工作到该公司在2008年11月停工。<ref name="Kates2"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.eweek.com/c/a/IT-Management/Binghamton-Gunman-is-Reportedly-Laid-Off-IBMer-408098/|title=IBM Denies Link to Binghamton Gunman|last=Taft|first=Darryl K.|date=April 3, 2009|publisher=eWEEK|accessdate=April 4, 2009}}</ref>事发前，王亦经常到移民服务中心上语言课，直到2009年3月初才中断学习。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.qq.com/a/20090405/000155.htm|title=纽约枪击案凶手作案或与英语差遭人耻笑有关|accessdate=2009-04-05|work=新华网|publisher=腾讯网|date=2009-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408173813/http://news.qq.com/a/20090405/000155.htm|archive-date=2009-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

王的作案动机目前并不完全清楚，可能与本人最近失业、在纽约很难找到工作和因[[英语|英语]]水平低而遭人耻笑等因素有关。<ref name="Kates2"/>据称王在吸尘器公司工作时，就曾对别人说过“I don't like America. America sucks.”（我不喜欢美国，美国很差），也曾提到过暗杀[[美国总统|美国总统]]的想法。<ref>{{cite news|last=Kemp|first=Joe|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/2009/04/04/2009-04-04_who_is_jiverly_voong_aka_jiverly_wong_co.html|title=Who is Jiverly Voong aka Jiverly Wong? Conflicting picture of Binghamton gunman emerges|publisher=New York Daily News|date=2009-04-04|accessdate=2009-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090407060151/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/2009/04/04/2009-04-04_who_is_jiverly_voong_aka_jiverly_wong_co.html|archive-date=2009-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事件过程==
2009年4月3日，吉韦利·王驾驶着以父亲名义登记的丰田，来到移民服务中心门口，用自己的车堵住服务中心后门，以确保没有人能从后门逃走，然后从前门进入服务中心。<ref name="Hostages Taken in Binghamton, N.Y.">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/04/nyregion/04hostage.html?_r=1&partner=MOREOVERNEWS&ei=5040|title=Hostages Taken in Binghamton, N.Y.|date=April 3, 2009|accessdate=April 3, 2009|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119185607/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/04/nyregion/04hostage.html?_r=1&partner=MOREOVERNEWS&ei=5040|archive-date=2016-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>据他人描述，王当时身着亮绿色的尼龙夹克、防弹背心，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gJkIIKfdTrpMZyiQPW7SWmCNR2HAD97BV6580|title=As NY gunman's life unraveled, he took others'|last=Rubinkam|first=Michael|date=2009-04-04|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=2009-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408071104/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gJkIIKfdTrpMZyiQPW7SWmCNR2HAD97BV6580|archive-date=2009-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>戴着深边眼镜，<ref name="FOX">{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,512476,00.html|title=Gunman Kills 13, Himself at Upstate New York Immigrant Center|last=Donaldson-Evans|first=Catherine|coauthors=Associated Press|date=April 3, 2009|publisher=Fox News|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406124723/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,512476,00.html|archive-date=2009-04-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>腰带上插着一把猎刀，<ref name="FOX" />一只手电筒，<ref name="qiaobaowang">{{cite news|url=http://www.chinapressusa.com/2009-04/03/content_204557.htm|title=宾汉姆顿枪击14人命案 凶手开枪动机不明|publisher=侨报网|date=2009-04-03|accessdate=2009-04-06}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>从前门进入移民服务中心后，一言不发，<ref name="WPost" />便朝前台接待员和前方的人开火。<ref name="Hostages Taken in Binghamton, N.Y."/>两名服务中心的人员中弹倒在血泊中，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5g8-DEMtAE9q4i4ySQ0eV_qZefmRQD97B83N81|title=AP Top News at 5:38 p.m.|date=April 3, 2009|publisher=The Associated Press|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406122859/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5g8-DEMtAE9q4i4ySQ0eV_qZefmRQD97B83N81|archive-date=2009-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中一人头部中弹，当场死亡；<ref name = "abcnews"/><ref name="WPost">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/04/03/AR2009040301774.html?hpid=topnews|title=Gunman Kills at Least 13 in Binghamton, N.Y.|last=Branigin|first=William|date=April 3, 2009|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203154842/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/04/03/AR2009040301774.html?hpid=topnews|archive-date=2016-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一名人员腹部中弹，<ref name="WPost" />装死倒下躲过一劫，并在凶手离开之后，躲到桌子下拨打911报警（此时为10:31<ref name="WPost" />）。<ref name="AP" />虽然伤势严重，这名接待员在报警后一直向警方传达信息，直至39分钟后自己获救。<ref name="Mercury">{{cite news|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/crime/ci_12068204|title=Gunman blocks N.Y. center's door, kills 13, self|author=William Kates|publisher=San Jose Mercury News|date=April 3, 2009|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195832/http://www.mercurynews.com/crime/ci_12068204|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="press"/>

凶手然后进入离前台不远的一间教室，朝里面正在上公民入籍课<ref name="WPost" /><ref name="AP" />的人群扫射，并挟持了一些人作为人质。<ref name="FOX"/>附近教室有26名学生，在听到枪声后，紧急躲到地下的锅炉房，躲过一劫。<ref name="qiaobaowang" /><ref name="Man shoots at least 12, takes 41 hostage in New York"/>

警方在接到报警后两分钟内便赶到出事现场，封锁现场、附近街道和[[宾厄姆顿高中|中学]]，<ref name="Man shoots at least 12, takes 41 hostage in New York">{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2009/0403/breaking57.htm|title=Man shoots at least 12, takes 41 hostage in New York|date=April 3, 2009|accessdate=April 3, 2009|publisher=The Irish Times}}</ref>要求民众避免接近现场，留在屋内不要外出。凶手在听到警笛声后，发现无路可逃，便饮弹自尽。<ref name="As gunman's life fell apart, he took others'">{{cite news|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090405/ap_on_re_us/binghamton_shootings|title=As gunman's life fell apart, he took others'|date=April 4, 2009|accessdate=April 4, 2009|publisher=[[Associated_Press|The Associated Press]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408164321/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090405/ap_on_re_us/binghamton_shootings|archive-date=2009-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>60-90分钟后警方进入服务中心。<ref name="As gunman's life fell apart, he took others'"/>这期间警方曾请{{le|布鲁姆社区学院|Broome Community College}}的越南裔助理教授阮相雄（Tuong Hung Nguyen）到场协助警方了解，该副教授能讲流利的[[越南话|越南话]]。<ref name="qiaobaowang" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.pressconnects.com/article/20090403/NEWS01/904030434|title=IBM denies Hinchey claim that shooter was laid off from IBM|publisher=Press Connect|date=April 3, 2009|accessdate=2009-04-06}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 

在数小时的搜寻之后，SWAT人员在当天下午2:33分，确认建筑物已安全，建筑物内除遗体外已经没有其他人。事件后警方请越南裔的当地高中老师黄诚（Thanh Huynh）为幸存的越南裔移民当翻译，帮助警方了解当时的情况。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/04/nyregion/04civic.html|title=In a Town With Few Immigrants, an Unlikely Horror|last=Fernandez|first=Manny|date=April 3, 2009|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409050801/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/04/nyregion/04civic.html|archive-date=2009-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

吉韦利·王的尸体被警方在服务中心的一楼发现，尸体上有自杀产生的枪弹伤痕。<ref name="FOX" /><ref name="AP">{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5iTkwh0jekRrls-b8ugkObNpK6XsQD97B7TGG0|title=Police: 14 killed in NY immigrant center shooting|last=Kates|first=William|date=April 3, 2009|publisher=The Associated Press|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406052426/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5iTkwh0jekRrls-b8ugkObNpK6XsQD97B7TGG0|archive-date=2009-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>死者脖子上还有一个小背包，包中有子弹，他身边还有两把半自动手枪。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/la-na-binghamton-shooting-hostage4-2009apr04,0,4181574.story|title=Binghamton, N.Y., gunman kills 13|last=Muskal|first=Michael|date=April 3, 2009|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=April 3, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210073851/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/la-na-binghamton-shooting-hostage4-2009apr04,0,4181574.story|archive-date=2019-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方根据其上面的序号，确认此人就是凶手吉韦利·王。<ref name="nytimesblog" />

发生事件的宾厄姆顿曾被评为“美国犯罪率最低的小镇之一”。<ref name="qiaobaowang" />事件发生后，当时正在欧洲进行访问的美国总统[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]，称这场枪击案为“毫无意义的暴力行为”（senseless violence），并对事件的发生感到震惊和悲伤。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5h4UWfyxeUBx8xanaSkirHYaK5ejwD97B7EH80|title=Obama calls shooting act of 'senseless violence'|date=2009-04-04|accessdate=2009-04-06|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406052425/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5h4UWfyxeUBx8xanaSkirHYaK5ejwD97B7EH80|archive-date=2009-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

